516
00:43:22,460 --> 00:43:28,099
[SPEAKER_00] Jer oni se i tekako dobro prilagode onome što Brisel naredi.

517
00:43:28,099 --> 00:43:31,159
[SPEAKER_00] I on je s ovim tarifama doveo prakčešnom predzivu

518
00:43:31,159 --> 00:43:34,960
