561
00:47:13,159 --> 00:47:18,159
[SPEAKER_00] i nije sposobno artikulirati bilo kakav cilj i strategiju

562
00:47:18,159 --> 00:47:22,159
[SPEAKER_00] kako doći do cilja Hrvatskog nareda u Bosni i Hercegovini,

563
00:47:22,159 --> 00:47:25,159
