580
00:48:25,159 --> 00:48:28,159
[SPEAKER_00] između Europske unije i Kanade?

581
00:48:28,159 --> 00:48:32,159
[SPEAKER_00] Kako mi to pojašnjavate ako veto nije evropska vrijednost?

582
00:48:32,159 --> 00:48:35,159
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, pa upravo ste.

583
00:48:35,159 --> 00:48:36,159
[SPEAKER_00] Aha.

584
00:48:36,159 --> 00:48:38,159
[SPEAKER_00] Kad im ponudite protuargument.

585
00:48:38,159 --> 00:48:40,159
